Package com.atakmap.android.gpx

Class Gpx

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.atakmap.android.gpx.Gpx
  • public class Gpx
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the top level GPX class with SimpleXML annotations to support serialization GPX gpxType GPX is the root element in the XML file. GPX documents contain a metadata header, followed by waypoints, routes, and tracks. You can add your own elements to the extensions section of the GPX document.
